These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, quad-bike, trike
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | helicopter | jet-ski | quad-bike | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, basketball, baseball, rugby
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Sport   | basketball | swimming | rugby | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
House: modern, gothic-revival, wooden, townhouse
1. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
2. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
3. the townhouse house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| House   | modern | wooden | gothic-revival | townhouse |

