.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, october, november, april
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in april##2
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Birthday   | april | october | september | november |

