2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | drawing | collecting | camping | reading |

