.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-12::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, rock, punk, jazz
1. the fan of punk is between the fan of jazz and the fan of rock##2
2. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | rock | punk | jazz | trance |

