1. the australian is on the left of the egyptian##1
2. the japanese is on the left of the malaysian##1
3. the egyptian is on the left or right of the australian##3
4. the malaysian is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Nationality   | japanese | malaysian | australian | egyptian |

 